{"tid":1644065,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（橋唔怕舊）小妹寫信撐警：多謝你們最近付出了這麼多的傷和累","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:24:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02207ed8264655e577538b061e287c4fa715dc2c","tid":1644065,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.speakout.hk/articles/cover/20191010/bc2a74d8bd3bdbe8ab6c3fb3b5126203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.speakout.hk%2Farticles%2Fcover%2F20191010%2Fbc2a74d8bd3bdbe8ab6c3fb3b5126203.jpg&h=c9b49c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一封多謝香港警察的公開信，一位名叫「Hannah」的小妹妹指，最近警察「付出了這麼多的傷和累」，又指他們「盡忠職守地保護香港」表達謝意。信中又指，示威者破壞地方及威脅市民的安全，身為「小市民」，見到警方「驅趕示威者，讓香港維持秩序」，表示「辛苦了」一班警察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小妹妹又窩心地「溫提」警員，即使再忙也要注意休息，指他們「要多吃一些飯，這樣才有力氣對抗示威者，要多喝水以免中暑」，最後再一次表示多謝和支持警方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：香港警察Facebook、網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.speakout.hk/港人花生/49554/-真心真意-小妹妹寫信撐警-多謝你們最近付出了這麼多的傷和累#selected</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9168d5ce3def66d4a76c38220d51d8833b5dd840","tid":1644065,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"對抗示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b539719d3422f09d3d4c90fe3689e1973e66151e","tid":1644065,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"跨界別抗爭籌備組： 致香港人的信&lt;You May Say I&rsquo;m a DREAMER&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1643981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1643981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PpqhE3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPpqhE3i.jpg&h=3d323244&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26be9bfae23fae1f8c727f04ee8002e93fafa102","tid":1644065,"uid":135871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"［國際文宣］你地唔